  "siteName": "歸藏的AI工具箱",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">上次分享完如何用 Claude 写出好看的界面之后发现，这套逻辑还能解决另一个打工人更加紧迫的问题。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(216, 57, 49);\"><span leaf=\"\">将文档变成更加易读的 PPT 或者网页</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。先来看一下效果。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">我找了一个 Stripe 24 年的总结文档，里面有他们的各种数据和优质客户的案例，但是全是密密麻麻的文字，而且全是英文。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100003932\" data-ratio=\"0.42407407407407405\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/295474e7-ccbf-4caa-006d-68ee18079800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/295474e7-ccbf-4caa-006d-68ee18079800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">生成之后的页面是这样的，Claude 会自动提取信息层级和分类，然后生成非常易于理解和美观的可视化网页，支持切换成夜间模式和移动端的响应式网页。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">你也可以在这个网址预览网页：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: #0052ff;\">https://lqb9jj5ryz.yourware.so/</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe videosnap_video_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-url=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzQb99jWibS1HpOSjGibeexXsnNWjgPjDTOn41mkCWeicH8viamTsfcEgyhp5H4I0LOAmu4eKjsMTrLHsvG9icxcj0iazA&amp;token=2lt8WBSnjTn6hZhJRXTNVNv4vjT8TvfKjic1tJ2URhVcRH5030LpGKYfrv21azyqf62kCcBMdyjkU0ZgA5PH7ibAIgtZB4edic7jibiciauibyDO7TMnThtYvY18ibP5eX9nLq0djv1q7ibcTtibEQNop9Oh7j6c98IP3GUnFI5P9eHcemsiaM&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=2\" data-headimgurl=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/EiaeLNTCu3EW3KLfetdWEbxibyLQIupbCeOmlKsfPL0LA/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c7eb8911c6d4cf00e432b077bc294083c45937fd15ae09793232d264@finder\" data-nickname=\"歸藏2079\" data-desc=\"新玩法 get，一套提示词将任何文档变成可视化网页\n这不比 PPT 和 PDF 更方便传播和理解？\n比如这个全是文字的 Stripe 年度报告 PDF 文件\n- 支持响应式设计、夜间模式切换\n- 一次成功无需调整\n以后随着模型能力增强估计内容展示方式也需要变化\n灵感来自 lepadphone 老师，你可以在这里预览这个网页：lqb9jj5ryz.yourware.so\n\" data-nonceid=\"7449072605878602745\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1440\" data-type=\"video\" data-id=\"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAcsgID1kn3AAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPErqNgYW53BbqJzNPgMIulEtazPzjlR8pK5jsF36do\"></mp-common-videosnap>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么做的呢？</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">其实大部分的技巧和提示词来自我前几天写的这个教程：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU0MDk3NTUxMA==&amp;mid=2247487561&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7272bf99f518bcb8ba55ad9d079896a0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">别再用AI写垃圾代码！4个技巧帮你用AI写出漂亮炫酷的应用</span></a></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">这里直接给提示词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">相较于上个教程，我又加了几条要求，确保你可以将任何文件扔进去，不需要一个字的修改就能生成美观的网页。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(20, 86, 240);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 30px;padding-left: 20px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">因为我们很多的文件都是英文的，所以我加了让他变成中文的要求</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">另外让他参考 Linear App 的设计语言，这个灵感来自 Padphone 老师</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">还有就是可以在页面加上你的社交媒体链接和你的名字，方便网页传播之后大家可以找到作者</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">去掉了 Unsplash 的图片要求，因为免费的 API 不太好查找对应的主题图片</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;margin-top:12px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;font-weight:400;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;border-top-right-radius:5px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-top-left-radius:5px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;height:30px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"height: 30px;line-height: 30px;margin-left: 10px;display: flex;\"><span style=\"width: 10px;height: 10px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(255, 95, 86);margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"width: 10px;height: 10px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(255, 189, 46);margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"width: 10px;height: 10px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(39, 201, 63);margin-top: 10px;\"></span></span></span>\n   <pre style=\"margin: 0px;\"><code style=\"padding:4px 15px 15px;border-bottom-left-radius:5px;display:block;overflow-x:auto;font-size:14px;border-bottom-right-radius:5px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.5;\"><span leaf=\"\">我会给你一个文件，分析内容，并将其转化为美观漂亮的中文可视化网页：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 内容要求</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;所有页面内容必须为简体中文</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;保持原文件的核心信息，但以更易读、可视化的方式呈现</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在页面底部添加作者信息区域，包含：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;作者姓名: [作者姓名]</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;社交媒体链接: 至少包含GitHub、Twitter/X、LinkedIn等主流平台</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;版权信息和年份</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 设计风格</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;整体风格参考Linear App的简约现代设计</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;使用清晰的视觉层次结构，突出重要内容</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;配色方案应专业、和谐，适合长时间阅读</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 技术规范</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;使用HTML5、TailwindCSS 3.0+（通过CDN引入）和必要的JavaScript</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;实现完整的深色/浅色模式切换功能，默认跟随系统设置</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;代码结构清晰，包含适当注释，便于理解和维护</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 响应式设计</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;页面必须在所有设备上（手机、平板、桌面）完美展示</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;针对不同屏幕尺寸优化布局和字体大小</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;确保移动端有良好的触控体验</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 图标与视觉元素</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;使用专业图标库如Font Awesome或Material Icons（通过CDN引入）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;根据内容主题选择合适的插图或图表展示数据</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;避免使用emoji作为主要图标</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 交互体验</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;添加适当的微交互效果提升用户体验：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;按钮悬停时有轻微放大和颜色变化</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;卡片元素悬停时有精致的阴影和边框效果</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;页面滚动时有平滑过渡效果</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; *</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;内容区块加载时有优雅的淡入动画</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 性能优化</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;确保页面加载速度快，避免不必要的大型资源</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;图片使用现代格式(WebP)并进行适当压缩</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;实现懒加载技术用于长页面内容</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">## 输出要求</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;提供完整可运行的单一HTML文件，包含所有必要的CSS和JavaScript</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;确保代码符合W3C标准，无错误警告</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;页面在不同浏览器中保持一致的外观和功能</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">请根据上传文件的内容类型（文档、数据、图片等），创建最适合展示该内容的可视化网页。</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">你说生成之后如何部署的问题，这个如果你用的 POE 或者 Claude 都可以直接分享在线版本的网页，如果你用的不是这两个的话，只需要访问</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">https://www.yourware.so/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">，然后将代码粘贴进去点 Deploy Code 就行。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100003931\" data-ratio=\"0.6861111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d8aac339-e969-4702-cf31-4753d4382d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d8aac339-e969-4702-cf31-4753d4382d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">我其实已经看到很多自媒体将这种方法生成的网页截图放在他们的视频里帮助用户理解了，比如口罩哥那里我就看到好几次，但是没有这么漂亮。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">所以这种方法不只是可以帮你在工作中汇报内容，也可以帮用户理解复杂逻辑的内容和文档。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">你也可以在提示词中加入你自己的需求，例如确实需要 PPT 形式的就可以让他生成网页形式的 PPT，每个卡片大小都是 16:9 的比例就行。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天的教程就到这里了，如果觉得对你有帮助的话麻烦给个赞👍或者喜欢🩷</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文介绍了如何利用 Claude AI 的强大功能，通过优化提示词，将复杂文档自动化转化为美观易读的可视化网页，从而显著提升工作效率和信息传播效果。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文介绍了如何利用 Claude AI 的强大功能，通过优化提示词，将复杂文档自动化转化为美观易读的可视化网页，从而显著提升工作效率和信息传播效果。",
